#<AdxTL>@(#)2.0.0.0 $Revision$
#**
#* =================================================================================
#* PHYELT_C_MPR : PHYELT Private Methods
#* =================================================================================
#* Fixes
# Issue X3-101936 - 2018-08-29 by FHA : Duplicating a Phy elt uses wrong ref counter
#* MDJ   21.07.2018 X3-102073 Physical element disposal: link  [V]CST_TSREPRI and RPHY_ISSTYP missing
#* CBO   15.09.2017 X3-55206 message's problem in transfer method : same on in other methods.
#* MWA   01.03.2017 121531   CIG activity code must be active to execute the involved statements.
#*
#* You will find hereunder a full desciption of PHYELT private methods, operations or functions.
#*   Methods    :
#*     - Check barcode unicity (_IS_BAC_UNIQUE)
#*     - Physical asset disposal (_PHYELT_ISSUE)
#*     - Cancellation of a physical asset disposal (_PHYELT_CNL_ISSUE)
#*     - Physical asset transfer (_PHYELT_TRANSFER)
#*     - Cancellation of a physical asset transfert (_PHYELT_CNL_TRANSFER)
#*     - Cancellation of the last pending movement(_PHYELT_CNL_LST_MVT)
#*     - Deletion of all pending movements(_PHYELT_DEL_ALL_MVT)
#*   Operations :
#*     - Physical asset disposal (_PHYELT_ISSUE_OPE)
#*     - Cancellation of a physical asset disposal (_PHYELT_CNL_ISSUE_OPE)
#*     - Physical asset transfer (_PHYELT_TRANSFER_OPE)
#*     - Physical asset stocktake (_UPD_STOCKTAKE)
#*     - Reset physical asset stocktake (_DEL_STOCKTAKE)
#*     - Duplicate physical asset ( _PHYELT_DUPLICATE )
#*   Functions :
#*     - Update ENAFLG (according to value parameter) of all physical assets linked to the fixed asset. (_UPD_PHY_ENAFLG_FROM_FAS)
#*     - Get reference of a physical asset linked to the fixed asset if it has a pending movement. (_GET_PHY_WITH_MVT_FROM_FAS)
#*     - Get physical asset reference linked to the fixed asset if it has a physical disposal or disposal cancellation movement. (_GET_PHY_WITH_ISS_MVT_FROM_FAS)
#*     - Get physical asset reference linked to the fixed asset if it has a physical transfer pending movement. (_GET_PHY_WITH_TRF_MVT_FROM_FAS)
#*     - Get number of physical assets of a filtered population. (_GET_SELECTED_PHY_NBR)
#*     - Get number of a physical asset in a location and the number of those whose stocktake date is not null. (_GET_LCT_PHY_NBR)
#*     - Get number of a physical asset in a building and the number of those whose stocktake date is not null. (_GET_BUI_PHY_NBR)
#*     - Turns a disposal reason of a fixed asset into the corresponding one for a physical asset. (_GET_PHY_ISSTYP_FROM_FAS)
#*     - Turns a disposal reason of a physical asset into the corresponding one for a fixed asset. (_GET_FAS_ISSTYP_FROM_PHY)
#*     - Get issue paramaters from all the physical assets of a filtered population. (_GET_ISSUE_PARAM_FROM_PHY)
#*     - Issue all the physical assets of a filtered population (_ISSUE_PHYELT_POPULATION)
#*     - Cancel the disposal of all the physical assets of a filtered population (_CNL_ISSUE_PHYELT_POPULATION)
#*     - Cancel the transfer of all the physical assets of a filtered population (_CNL_TRANSFERT_PHYELT_POPULATION)
#* _______________________________________________________________________________
#*
#*!
#TODO: Refactor following methods
# _PHYELT_ISSUE to                  _ISSUE
# _PHYELT_CNL_ISSUE to              _CANCEL_ISSUE
# _PHYELT_TRANSFER to               _TRANSFER
# _PHYELT_CNL_TRANSFER to           _CANCEL_TRANSFER
# _PHYELT_ISSUE_CNL_LST_MVT to      _ISSUE_CANCEL_LAST_MOVEMENT
# _PHYELT_DEL_ALL_MVT to            _DELETE_ALL_MOVEMENT
# _PHYELT_ISSUE_OPE to              _ISSUE_OPE
# _PHYELT_CNL_ISSUE_OPE to          _CANCEL_ISSUE_OPE
# _PHYELT_TRANSFER_OPE to           _TRANSFER_OPE
# _PHYELT_CNL_TRANSFER_OPE to       _CANCEL_TRANSFER_OPE
# _PHYELT_ISSUE_CNL_LST_MVT_OPE to  _ISSUE_CANCEL_LAST_MOVEMENT_OPE
# _UPD_STOCKTAKE to                 _UPDATE_STOCKTAKE
# _DEL_STOCKTAKE to                 _DELETE_STOCKTAKE

$METHODS
  Case [L]CURPTH
    When ""
      Case [L]AMETHOD
        When "_IS_BAC_UNIQUE"                : Gosub _IS_BAC_UNIQUE                :   # BAC unicity
        When "_PHYELT_ISSUE"                 : Gosub _PHYELT_ISSUE                 :   # Physical asset issue
        When "_PHYELT_CNL_ISSUE"             : Gosub _PHYELT_CNL_ISSUE             :   # Cancel physical asset issue
        When "_PHYELT_TRANSFER"              : Gosub _PHYELT_TRANSFER              :   # Physical asset transfer
        When "_PHYELT_CNL_TRANSFER"          : Gosub _PHYELT_CNL_TRANSFER          :   # Cancel physical asset transfer
        When "_PHYELT_DEL_ALL_MVT"           : Gosub _PHYELT_DEL_ALL_MVT           :   # All pending movement deletion
        When "_PHYELT_ISSUE_CNL_LST_MVT"     : Gosub _PHYELT_ISSUE_CNL_LST_MVT     :   # Abandon last pending movement
        When "_PHYELT_ISSUE_MANAGEMENT"      : Gosub _PHYELT_ISSUE_MANAGEMENT      :   # Manages issuing and issue canceling
        When "_PHYELT_TRANSFER_MANAGEMENT"   : Gosub _PHYELT_TRANSFER_MANAGEMENT   :   # Manages transfer
        When "_CANCEL"                       : Gosub _CANCEL                       :   # Do nothing

        #-------------
        When Default  : Gosub METHODS From PHYELT_C_MPU
      Endcase
    When Default
  Endcase
Return

$OPERATIONS
  Case [L]CURPTH
    When ""
      Case [L]AOPERATION
        When "_PHYELT_ISSUE_OPE"             : Gosub _PHYELT_ISSUE_OPE             :   # Physical asset issue
        When "_PHYELT_CNL_ISSUE_OPE"         : Gosub _PHYELT_CNL_ISSUE_OPE         :   # Cancel physical asset issue
        When "_PHYELT_TRANSFER_OPE"          : Gosub _PHYELT_TRANSFER_OPE          :   # Physical asset transfer
        When "_PHYELT_CNL_TRANSFER_OPE"      : Gosub _PHYELT_CNL_TRANSFER_OPE      :   # Cancel physical asset transfer
        When "_PHYELT_ISSUE_CNL_LST_MVT_OPE" : Gosub _PHYELT_ISSUE_CNL_LST_MVT_OPE :   # Cancel physical asset transfer
        When "_UPD_STOCKTAKE"                : Gosub _UPD_STOCKTAKE                :   # Update stocktake data
        When "_DEL_STOCKTAKE"                : Gosub _DEL_STOCKTAKE                :   # Delete stocktake data
        When "_PHYELT_DUPLICATE_OPE"         : Gosub _PHYELT_DUPLICATE_OPE :               # Duplicate physical assrt
        #-------------
        When Default  : Gosub OPERATIONS From PHYELT_C_MPU
      Endcase
    When Default
  Endcase
Return

# ======================================================================
#    P R I V A T E    M E T H O D S
# ======================================================================

#**
#* Is the barcode is unique
#*
#* This method checks if barecode is unique inside the folder or the company according to CPYBACUNY parameter value.
#*
#* @private
#* @param R_BAC_UNIQUE : Return CST_ATRUE if code is unique, CST_AFALSE
#* @param RPHYREF : Return the reference of the physical element if code is non unique
#* @return ARET_VALUE : [V]CST_AOK if OK, else [V]CST_AERROR (check error message stack)
#*!
$_IS_BAC_UNIQUE
  ARET_VALUE = [V]CST_AOK
  RPHYREF = AVOID.ACHAR

  If this.BAC = AVOID.ACHAR
    #**
    #* ==> Barecode field parameter value is mandatory to execute that function
    #*!
    R_BAC_UNIQUE = [V]CST_AFALSE
    ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(61, [V]CST_MSGMIS, 1), [V]CST_AERROR)
    Return
  Endif

  Local File PHYELT [PHY]

  If (fmet this.ACTX.APARAM.AGETVALNUM([V]CST_ALEVFLD, "", "CPYBACUNY") = [V]CST_AYES)
    Filter [F:PHY] Where BAC = this.BAC and CPY = this.CPY and PHYREF <> this.PHYREF
  Else
    Filter [F:PHY] Where BAC = this.BAC and PHYREF <> this.PHYREF
  Endif
  Read [F:PHY]PHY3 First
  If fstat = [V]CST_AOK
    R_BAC_UNIQUE = [V]CST_AFALSE
    RPHYREF = [F:PHY]PHYREF
  Else
    R_BAC_UNIQUE = [V]CST_ATRUE
  Endif

  LogicClose File [F:PHY]

  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")

Return

#**
#* =============================
#* Private Method: _PHYELT_ISSUE  -  Physical asset disposal
#* -----------------------------
#* Physical asset disposal.
#*      A - Physical asset is not linked to a fixed asset
#*          The physical asset is modified with the disposal date and reason (ISSDAT, ISSTYP)
#*          and an event of disposal for the physical asset is created
#*      B - Physical is linked to a fixed asset
#*          A pending movement for validation of the disposal is generated
#*          with the disposal reason (MVTISSTYP) and the disposal date (MVTDAT)
#* -------------------------------
#* @private
#* @param  PARAM  : PHYELTISS data class instance contains parameters
#* @param            ISSDAT : Disposal date
#* @param            ISSTYP : Disposal reason
#* @param            FASFLG :
#* @return ARET_VALUE : [V]CST_AOK if OK, else [V]CST_AERROR (check error message stack)
#*!
$_PHYELT_ISSUE
  Local Integer STA
  Local Integer BRET
  ARET_VALUE= [V]CST_AOK

  this.PHYISS = [V]CST_ATRUE

  #--------------
  # Control
  #--------------

  If not (this.ISSDAT = AVOID.ADATE )
    #**
    #* ==> A physical asset cannot be disposed twice
    #*!
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(149,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
  Endif
  If not (PARAM.ISSDAT <> AVOID.ADATE)
    #**
    #* ==> The issue date is mandatory.
    #*!
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(151,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
  Endif
  If not (find(PARAM.ISSTYP, [V]CST_PDIVYISS, [V]CST_PDSALES, [V]CST_PDSCRAP, [V]CST_PDSTOLDI) > AVOID.AINT)
    #**
    #* ==> Valid issue reasons are : "Inventory disposal", "Sales", "Scrap" or "Stolen or disappeared
    #*!
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(150,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
  Endif

  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")
  If ([L]ARET_VALUE >= [V]CST_AERROR) : Return : Endif

  If (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET())
    # Physical asset linked to a fixed asset
    Local Integer I_ISSMVT, B_FOUND
    [L]B_FOUND = func _PHYMVT_FIND_MVT(this, [V]CST_PMVISS, [L]I_ISSMVT)
    If (B_FOUND = [V]CST_ATRUE and PARAM.FASFLG = [V]CST_ANO)
      #**
      #* ==> If the physical asset is linked to a fixed asset and a pending disposal movement exists
      #*     and issue is asked by physical element then no more disposal can be processed.
      #*!
      [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(154,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
    Endif
    If not (func PHYELT_CSTD._IS_ASSET_ENABLED(this) = [V]CST_AYES)
      #**
      #* ==> If the physical asset is linked to a fixed asset, the fixed asset must be "active",
      #*     otherwise, it cannot be disposed
      #*!
      [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(152,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
    Endif

#TODO: Create an method/operation on FXDASSETS class to know if fixed asset is not belong to a intra group transfer
    If func AFNC.ACTIV("CIG") : # FQ121531
      Local File CIGFXDSOR [CIB_]
      Read [CIB_]CIB4 = AASREF
      If fstat = [V]CST_AOK
        #**
        #* ==> If the physical asset is linked to a fixed asset, the fixed asset must not belong to an intra group transfer.
        #*!
        [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(153,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
      Endif
      LogicClose File [CIB_]
    Endif : # FQ121531

    Local Integer LIN
    Local Date    LSTTRFMVT_DAT
    # Evaluate : transfer date of the last pending transfer movement
#    [L]LSTTRFMVT_DAT = AVOID.ADATE
#    For [L]LIN =1 To maxtab(this.PHYMVT)
#      If this.PHYMVT([L]LIN) <> null and find(this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).ASTALIN,[V]CST_ADEL,[V]CST_ANEWDEL) = 0
#        If (this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVT = [V]CST_PMVGEO) : [L]LSTTRFMVT_DAT = this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTDAT : Endif
#      Endif
#    Next [L]LIN
    Local Date DATMAX
    # Evaluate : transfer date of the last pending transfer movement
    [L]BRET = func _PHYMVT_GET_MVTDAT_LAST(this, [V]CST_PMVGEO, [L]LSTTRFMVT_DAT)
    # Compare disposal date with transfer date
    [L]DATMAX = max([L]LSTTRFMVT_DAT, this.TRFDAT, this.DNUMRECEP)
    If not (PARAM.ISSDAT >= [L]DATMAX)
      #**
      #* ==> If the physical asset is linked to a fixed asset, the issue date must be greater or equal to
      #*     MAX ( Effective transfer date, date of the last pending transfer movement, receipt date).
      #*!
      [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(18,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1)-num$([L]DATMAX), [V]CST_AERROR)
    Endif
  Endif

  If not (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET())
    Local Date DATMAX
    [L]DATMAX = max(this.TRFDAT, this.DNUMRECEP)
    If not (PARAM.ISSDAT >= [L]DATMAX)
      #**
      #* ==> If the physical asset is NOT linked to a fixed asset, the issue date must be greater or equal to
      #*     MAX ( Effective transfer date, receipt date).
      #*!
      [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(18,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1)-num$([L]DATMAX), [V]CST_AERROR)
    Endif
  Endif

  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")
  If ([L]ARET_VALUE >= [V]CST_AERROR) : Return : Endif

  #--------------
  # Execution
  #--------------

  # Applying parameter values
  If (not (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET()) or PARAM.FASFLG = [V]CST_AYES)
    # NOT linked to a fixed assset
    this.ISSDAT    = PARAM.ISSDAT
    this.ISSTYP    = PARAM.ISSTYP
  Endif
  If (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET() and PARAM.FASFLG = [V]CST_ANO)
    # Linked to a fixed asset
    this.ISSDAT    = AVOID.ADATE
    this.ISSTYP    = [V]CST_PDNOTISS
  Endif

  # Physical asset not linked to a fixed asset
  If (not (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET()) or PARAM.FASFLG = [V]CST_AYES)
    # Event : Disposal of a physical asset
    Local Char EVT_ERRMSG(250)
    Local Instance EVT Using C_EVENT : EVT = NewInstance C_EVENT AllocGroup null
    EVT.EVTINT  = "PHYISS"
    [L]STA = fmet EVT.INIT_EVENT()

    EVT.REF     = this.PHYREF
    # Common event data
    EVT.EFFDAT  = PARAM.ISSDAT
    EVT.ACCDAT  = PARAM.ISSDAT
    EVT.ISSTYP  = PARAM.ISSTYP

    If not (fmet EVT.CRT_EVENT_PHY(this) = [V]CST_AOK)
      # Error when creating physical asset event.
      [L]ARET_VALUE = func FXDFCT_SYRA.COPY_MSG(EVT, this)
      [L]ARET_VALUE = [V]CST_AERROR
    Endif

    FreeGroup EVT
  Endif

  # Physical asset linked to a fixed asset
  If (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET())
    If (PARAM.FASFLG = [V]CST_AYES)
      # Via Fixed asset
      # Pending movement for validation of the disposal (if it exists) must be deleted
      Local Integer I_MVT, B_FOUND
      [L]B_FOUND = func _PHYMVT_FIND_MVT(this, [V]CST_PMVISS, [L]I_MVT)
      If ([L]B_FOUND)
        [L]STA = fmet this.ADELLINE("PHYMVT", [L]I_MVT)
        [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(173,[V]CST_MSGPHY, 1), [V]CST_ASUCCESS)
      Endif
      # Issue 110486
      # Delete Also transfer mvt and cancelled transfer
      [L]B_FOUND = func _PHYMVT_FIND_MVT(this, [V]CST_PMVGEO, [L]I_MVT)
      If ([L]B_FOUND)
        [L]STA = fmet this.ADELLINE("PHYMVT", [L]I_MVT)
        [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(173,[V]CST_MSGPHY, 1), [V]CST_ASUCCESS)
      Endif
      [L]B_FOUND = func _PHYMVT_FIND_MVT(this, [V]CST_PMVAGEO, [L]I_MVT)
      If ([L]B_FOUND)
        [L]STA = fmet this.ADELLINE("PHYMVT", [L]I_MVT)
        [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(173,[V]CST_MSGPHY, 1), [V]CST_ASUCCESS)
      Endif
      # End Issue 110486
    Else
      # Via Physical asset
      Local Integer LIN
      # Pending movement for validation of the disposal must be generated
      [L]LIN= fmet this.ADDLINE("PHYMVT",[V]CST_ALASTPOS)
      this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).NUM       = [L]LIN
      this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVT       = [V]CST_PMVISS
      this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTDAT    = PARAM.ISSDAT
      this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTTRANS  = AVOID.ACHAR
      this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTFCY    = AVOID.ACHAR
      this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTLCTCOD = AVOID.ACHAR
      this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTISSTYP = PARAM.ISSTYP

      [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(13,[V]CST_MSGPHY, 1), [V]CST_AWARNING)
    Endif
  Endif

  # X3-55206
  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")

  If ([L]ARET_VALUE < [V]CST_AWARNING)
    Local Char ERRMSG(250)
    [L]ERRMSG = func ASYRFNC.MES1(mess(170,[V]CST_MSGPHY, 1), this.PHYREF)
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", [L]ERRMSG, [V]CST_ASUCCESS)
  Endif

  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")

Return

#**
#* =================================
#* Private Method: _PHYELT_CNL_ISSUE - Physical asset disposal cancellation.
#* ---------------------------------
#* Disposal cancellation for a physical element that is "effectivly" disposed.
#*      A - Physical asset is not linked to a fixed asset
#*          The physical asset is modified. The disposal date and reason are cleared (ISSDAT, ISSTYP)
#*          and an event to reverse the physical asset disposal event is created
#*      B - Physical is linked to a fixed asset
#*          i  - a pending movement for validation of the disposal exists. This movement is deleted
#*          ii - no pending movement, the physical asset is effectivily disposed.
#*               A pending movement for validation of the disposal cancellation is created
#* ---------------------------------
#* @private
#* @param  PARAM : PHYELTISS data class instance contains parameters
#* @return ARET_VALUE : [V]CST_AOK if OK, else [V]CST_AERROR (check error message stack)
#*!
$_PHYELT_CNL_ISSUE
  Local Integer STA, I_ISSMVT
  Local Integer B_MVTFOUND, WMVT, WORDER

  [L]ARET_VALUE= [V]CST_AOK

   this.PHYCNLISS = [V]CST_ATRUE

  #--------------
  # Control
  #--------------
  # Physical asset NOT linked to a fixed asset
  If not (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET())
    If not (this.ISSDAT <> AVOID.ADATE)
      #**
      #* ==> If the physical asset is not linked to a fixed asset, it must have been disposed for cancelling disposal.
      #*     Therefore disposal date must be filled (ISSDAT)
      #*!
      [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(155,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
    Endif
  Endif

  # Physical asset linked to a fixed asset
  If (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET())
    [L]B_MVTFOUND = func _PHYMVT_GET_MVT_LAST(this, WMVT, WORDER)

    If (this.ISSDAT = AVOID.ADATE)
#      #**
#      #* ==> If the physical asset is linked to a fixed asset, the physical asset must be disposed for cancelling disposal.
#      #*     Therefore disposal date must be filled
#      #*     ISSDAT if the physical asset has been effectively disposed
#      #*!
#      [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(155,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)

      If ([L]B_MVTFOUND <> [V]CST_ATRUE)
        #**
        #* ==> If there is no pending movement, no cancellation can be processed.
        #*!
        [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(160,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
      Endif
      If [L]B_MVTFOUND = [V]CST_ATRUE and not (WMVT = [V]CST_PMVISS)
        #**
        #* ==> If it's asked to delete a disposal movement and the last pending movement isn't one. Deletion cannot be processed.
        #*!
        [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(223,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
      Endif
    Endif

    # Fixed asset is effectively issued
    If (this.ISSDAT <> AVOID.ADATE and PARAM.FASFLG = [V]CST_ANO)
      If not (this.ISSDAT >= fmet this.ACTX.ACACHE.CNX.AGETVALDAT(this.CPY, 1, "CURFIYSTR"))
        #**
        #* ==> If the physical asset is effectivily disposed (ei ISSDAT is filled),
        #*     the disposal must not have been carried out in a previous fiscal year
        #*     Therefore the disposal date must be greater than or equal to
        #*     the beginning of the current fiscal year of the finance context .
        #*!
        [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(11,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
      Endif
      If ([L]B_MVTFOUND = [V]CST_ATRUE and WMVT = [V]CST_PMVAISS) Then
        #**
        #* ==> If the physical asset is effectivily disposed (ei ISSDAT is filled),
        #*     if a cancelation disposal pending movement exists it cannot be cancelled twice
        #*!
        [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(178,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
      Endif
    Endif

  Endif

  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")
  If ([L]ARET_VALUE >= [V]CST_AERROR) : Return : Endif

  #--------------
  # Execution
  #--------------
  # Physical asset NOT linked to a fixed asset
  If (not (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET()) or PARAM.FASFLG = [V]CST_AYES )
    # Event reversal : Disposal of a physical asset
    Local Char EVT_ERRMSG(250)
    Local Instance EVT Using C_EVENT : EVT = NewInstance C_EVENT AllocGroup null

      EVT.EVTINT  = "PHYISS"
      [L]STA = fmet EVT.INIT_EVENT()

      EVT.REF     = this.PHYREF
      EVT.CPY     = this.CPY
      EVT.LIN     = 0
      EVT.PLAN    = [V]CST_PLNAUC
      EVT.EFFDAT  = this.ISSDAT

      # Reversal of issue event
      If not fmet EVT.EXT_EVENT() = [V]CST_AOK
        # Error when reversing physical asset event.
        [L]ARET_VALUE = func FXDFCT_SYRA.COPY_MSG(EVT, this)
        [L]ARET_VALUE = [V]CST_AERROR
      Endif

    FreeGroup EVT
  Endif

  # Physical asset linked to a fixed asset
  If (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET())
    If (this.ISSDAT = AVOID.ADATE or PARAM.FASFLG <> [V]CST_ANO)
#      # Demande physique d'une annulation de sortie ou refus comptable d'une sortie physique
#      [L]I_ISSMVT = func _PHYMVT_FIND_MVT(this, [V]CST_PMVISS)
#      If [L]I_ISSMVT = 0
#        # Validation comptable de l'annulation d'une sortie
#        [L]I_ISSMVT = func _PHYMVT_FIND_MVT(this, [V]CST_PMVAISS)
#      Endif
#      If [L]I_ISSMVT > 0
      If [L]B_MVTFOUND = [V]CST_ATRUE
        # Pending movement for validation of the disposal must be deleted
        # - Demande physique d'une annulation de sortie
        # - Refus comptable d'une sortie physique
        # - Validation comptable de l'annulation d'une sortie
        [L]STA = fmet this.ADELLINE("PHYMVT", WORDER)
      Endif
    Endif

    If (this.ISSDAT <> AVOID.ADATE and PARAM.FASFLG = [V]CST_ANO)
      # Pending movement for validation of the disposal cancellation must be generated
      Local Integer LIN
      [L]LIN = fmet this.ADDLINE("PHYMVT", [V]CST_ALASTPOS)
      this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).NUM       = [L]LIN
      this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVT       = [V]CST_PMVAISS
      this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTDAT    = this.ISSDAT
      this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTTRANS  = AVOID.ACHAR
      this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTFCY    = AVOID.ACHAR
      this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTLCTCOD = AVOID.ACHAR
      this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTISSTYP = this.ISSTYP

      [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(224,[V]CST_MSGPHY, 1), [V]CST_AWARNING)
    Endif
  Endif

  # Applying values for cancellation
  If (not (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET()) or PARAM.FASFLG = [V]CST_AYES)
    # NOT linked to a fixed assset
    this.ISSDAT = AVOID.ADATE
    this.ISSTYP = [V]CST_PDNOTISS
  Endif

  # Issue 110771
  If [L]B_MVTFOUND = [V]CST_ATRUE and WMVT = [V]CST_PMVISS
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(173,[V]CST_MSGPHY, 1), [V]CST_ASUCCESS)
  Endif

  # X3-55206
  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")

  If(fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("") < [V]CST_AWARNING)
  #If ([L]ARET_VALUE < [V]CST_AWARNING)
  # End issue 110771
    Local Char ERRMSG(250)
    [L]ERRMSG = func ASYRFNC.MES1(mess(172,[V]CST_MSGPHY, 1), this.PHYREF)
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", [L]ERRMSG, [V]CST_ASUCCESS)
  Endif

  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")

Return

#**
#* Last pending movement cancellation.
#*
#* If the physical asset is linked to a fixed asset, the last pending movement is deleted if it exists.
#*
#* @private
#* @return ARET_VALUE : [V]CST_AOK if OK, else [V]CST_AERROR (check error message stack)
#*!
$_PHYELT_ISSUE_CNL_LST_MVT

  Local Integer STA
  Local Char ERRMSG(250)
  Local Integer WMVT, WORDER

  [L]ARET_VALUE = [V]CST_AOK

  #--------------
  # Control
  #--------------

  [L]STA = func _PHYMVT_GET_MVT_LAST(this, WMVT, WORDER)

  If ([L]STA <> [V]CST_ATRUE)
    #**
    #* ==> If there is no pending movement, no cancellation can be processed.
    #*!
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(160,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
  Endif
  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")
  If ([L]ARET_VALUE >= [V]CST_AERROR) : Return : Endif

  If (not (WMVT = [V]CST_PMVAISS)) Then
    #**
    #* ==> If it's asked to delete a cancellation disposal movement and the last pending movement isn't one. Deletion cannot be processed.
    #*!
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(221,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
  Endif
  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")
  If ([L]ARET_VALUE >= [V]CST_AERROR) : Return : Endif

  #--------------
  # Execution
  #--------------

#  If (WMVT = [V]CST_PMVISS) Then
#    # If the deleted movement is a disposal one, the picture of disposal is cleared.
#    this.ISSPCT = AVOID.ABLOB
#  Endif

  # Last movement deletion
  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ADELLINE("PHYMVT", [L]WORDER)

  # X3-55206
  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")

  If [L]ARET_VALUE < [V]CST_AERROR
    Local Char ERRMSG(250)
    [L]ERRMSG = func ASYRFNC.MES1(mess(173,[V]CST_MSGPHY, 1), this.PHYREF)
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", [L]ERRMSG, [V]CST_ASUCCESS)
  Endif

  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")

Return

#**
#* ================================
#* Private Method: _PHYELT_TRANSFER - Physical asset transfer.
#* --------------------------------
#* Physical asset transfer of location.
#*      A - Physical asset is not linked to a fixed asset
#*          The physical asset is modified : Transfer date (TRFDAT), New location (LCTCOD), New Facility (FCY)
#*          and an event of transfer for the physical asset is created
#*      B - The physical asset is linked to a fixed asset
#*          i  - No financial facility transfer induced
#*               (ei. The physical asset is transfered into a location in the same financial facility)
#*               if no pending movement exists
#*                  - The physical asset is modified:
#*                    Transfer date (TRFDAT), New location (LCTCOD), New Facility (FCY)
#*                  - An event of transfer for the physical asset is created
#*          ii - Financial facility transfer induced
#*               (ei. The physical asset is transfered into a location of another financial facility)
#*               if no pending disposal movement exists
#*               a pending movement for validation of the transfer is generated
#*               containing the transfer information to validate.
#* --------------------------------
#* @private
#* @param  PARAM   : PHYELTTRF data class instance contains parameters
#* @param             TRFDAT    : Transfer date
#* @param             TRFTYP    : Transfer reason
#* @param             TRFLCTCOD : New location
#* @param             FASFLG    :
#* @param             ORIACT    :
#* @return Integer : ARET_VALUE = [V]CST_AOK, [V]CST_AINFO, [V]CST_ASUCESS, [V]CST_AERROR, [V]CST_AFATAL
#*!
$_PHYELT_TRANSFER

  Local Char ERRMSG(250), FCYD(GLONFCY), CPYD(GLONCPY)
  Local Integer STA, BRET, LIN, WMVT
  Local Integer B_FINANCIAL_TRF
  Local Date LSTTRFMVT_DAT

  [L]ARET_VALUE = [V]CST_AOK
  this.PHYTRF = [V]CST_ATRUE

  #--------------
  # Control
  #--------------

  If not (PARAM.TRFDAT <> AVOID.ADATE)
    #**
    #* ==> For transfer to be allowed, transfer date must be entered
    #*!
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(176,[V]CST_MSGPHY, 1), [V]CST_AERROR)
  Endif
  If not (PARAM.TRFTYP <> AVOID.ACHAR)
    #**
    #* ==> For transfer to be allowed, transfer reason must be entered
    #*!
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(177,[V]CST_MSGPHY, 1), [V]CST_AERROR)
  Endif
  If not (PARAM.TRFLCTCOD <> AVOID.ACHAR)
    #**
    #* ==> For transfer to be allowed, location must be entered
    #*!
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(85,[V]CST_MSGPHY, 1), [V]CST_AERROR)
  Endif

  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")
  If ([L]ARET_VALUE >= [V]CST_AERROR) : Return : Endif

  If not (this.LCTCOD <> PARAM.TRFLCTCOD)
    If (PARAM.ORIACT <> [V]CST_OAFASTRFPHY)
      #**
      #* ==> Target location must be different from the original one.
      #*!
      [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(3,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AWARNING)
    Endif
  Endif

#TODO: Add the control on CIG like issue (only financial transfer)

  # Return if AWARNING
  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")
  If ([L]ARET_VALUE >= [V]CST_AWARNING) : Return : Endif

  If not (PARAM.TRFDAT > this.DNUMRECEP)
    #**
    #* ==> The transfer date must be greater than reception date, if it has been filled
    #*!
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(161,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
  Endif

  # If it's not a financial transfer, there will not write movement : always transfer will be done
  [L]B_FINANCIAL_TRF = func IS_FINANCIAL_TRANSFER(this, PARAM.TRFLCTCOD, [L]FCYD, [L]CPYD, [L]LSTTRFMVT_DAT)

  If not (this.CPY = [L]CPYD)
    #**
    #* ==> Transfer must take place in the same company,
    #*     companies of the target location and the original one must be equal.
    #*!
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(157, [V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
  Endif

  If not (this.ISSDAT = AVOID.ADATE)
    #**
    #* ==> A physical asset cannot be transfered if it is effectively issued (ISSDAT is filled).
    #*!
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(156,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
  Endif

  # Physical asset linked to a fixed asset
#  If (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET()) # Issue 110604
    If not (PARAM.TRFDAT > this.TRFDAT)
      #* When cancelling transfer from a fixed assets,
      #* the physical asset is transfered to its original location at the same date
      #* So in this case only in this one, the transfer date can be equal to the last effective transfer date
      If PARAM.FASFLG = [V]CST_ANO or (PARAM.ORIACT = [V]CST_OAFASCTRFPHY and PARAM.TRFDAT < this.TRFDAT)
        #**
        #* ==> If the physical asset is linked to a fixed asset,
        #*     the transfer date must be greater than the last effective transfert date
        #*!
        [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(162,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
      Endif
    Endif

  If (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET()) # Issue 110604
    If not (func PHYELT_CSTD._IS_ASSET_ENABLED(this) = [V]CST_AYES)
      #**
      #* ==> If the physical asset is linked to a fixed asset, the fixed asset must be "active",
      #*     otherwise it cannot be transferred
      #*!
      [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(165, [V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
    Endif

    If not (PARAM.TRFDAT > [L]LSTTRFMVT_DAT) and PARAM.FASFLG <> [V]CST_AYES
      #**
      #* ==> If the physical asset is linked to a fixed asset, the transfer date must be greater than
      #*     the transfer date of the last pending transfer movement if it exists one.
      #*!
      [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(163,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
    Endif

    # NOT a financial transfer
    # CFF-GLE 6/7/2015 : Unauthorized successive transfers
    # If [L]B_FINANCIAL_TRF = [V]CST_AFALSE and PARAM.FASFLG <> [V]CST_AYES
    If PARAM.FASFLG = [V]CST_ANO
      If (func _COLL_GET_COUNTTAB(this, "PHYMVT") > 0)
        #**
        #* ==> If the physical asset is linked to a fixed asset and the financial facility is unchanged
        #*     and a pending movement exists then the physical asset cannot be transfered
        #*!
        [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(158,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
      Endif
    Endif

    # Financial transfer
    If ([L]B_FINANCIAL_TRF = [V]CST_ATRUE)
      If func _COLL_FIND_MVT(this, "PHYMVT", [V]CST_PMVISS) = [V]CST_ATRUE
        #**
        #* ==> If the physical asset is linked to a fixed asset and the financial facility is changed
        #*     and a pending disposal movement exists then the physical asset cannot be transfered
        #*!
        [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(159,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
      Endif
    Endif
  Endif

  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")
  If ([L]ARET_VALUE >= [V]CST_AERROR) : Return : Endif

  #--------------
  # Execution
  #--------------

  # Applying parameter values
  If (not (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET()) or PARAM.FASFLG = [V]CST_AYES)
    # NOT linked to a fixed assset
    this.TRFDAT = PARAM.TRFDAT
    this.FCY    = [L]FCYD
    this.LCTCOD = PARAM.TRFLCTCOD
  Endif
  If (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET())
    # Linked to a fixed asset
    If ( [L]B_FINANCIAL_TRF = [V]CST_AFALSE )
      # Not a financial transfer
      this.TRFDAT = PARAM.TRFDAT
      this.FCY    = [L]FCYD
      this.LCTCOD = PARAM.TRFLCTCOD
    Endif
  Endif

  # Delete transfer (or ancel transfer) pending movement.
  # Case only of asset validation, because physical origin is check before
  [L]LIN = func _COLL_FIND_MVT(this, "PHYMVT", [V]CST_PMVGEO)
  If [L]LIN = [V]CST_ANOTDEFINED
    # Asset validation : case of non tranfer validation but cancel transfer
    [L]LIN = func _COLL_FIND_MVT(this, "PHYMVT", [V]CST_PMVAGEO)
  Endif
  If [L]LIN <> [V]CST_ANOTDEFINED
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ADELLINE("PHYMVT", [L]LIN)
    [L]ERRMSG = func ASYRFNC.MES1(mess(193, [V]CST_MSGPHY, 1), this.PHYREF)
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", [L]ERRMSG, [V]CST_ASUCCESS)
  Endif

  # If it's a Financial transfer and the Physical element is linked to an asset and it's not a validation (from assets) :
  # We must create a movement.
  # In each other cases, we create an event
  If (([L]B_FINANCIAL_TRF = [V]CST_ATRUE) and (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET()) and (PARAM.FASFLG <> [V]CST_AYES))
    # From PHY - Creating pending movement for validation
    [L]LIN = fmet this.ADDLINE("PHYMVT",[V]CST_ALASTPOS)
    this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).NUM       = [L]LIN
    this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVT       = [V]CST_PMVGEO
    this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTDAT    = PARAM.TRFDAT
    this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTTRANS  = PARAM.TRFTYP
    this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTFCY    = [L]FCYD
    this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTLCTCOD = PARAM.TRFLCTCOD
    # this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTISSTYP = 0
  Else
    # Create event
    Local Char EVT_ERRMSG(250)
    Local Instance EVT Using C_EVENT : EVT = NewInstance C_EVENT AllocGroup null
    EVT.EVTINT = "PHYAFFGEO"
    [L]STA = fmet EVT.INIT_EVENT()
    EVT.REF    = this.PHYREF
    # Common event data
    EVT.EFFDAT = PARAM.TRFDAT
    EVT.ACCDAT = PARAM.TRFDAT
    # Specific event data
    EVT.REN    = PARAM.TRFTYP

    [L]STA = fmet EVT.CRT_EVENT_PHY(this)
    [L]BRET = func FXDFCT_SYRA.COPY_MSG(EVT, this)
    If [L]STA <> [V]CST_AOK
      # Error when creating physical asset event.
      [L]ARET_VALUE = [V]CST_AERROR
    Endif
    FreeGroup EVT

    # Issue 110304 & 114755
    # put the same GEOLOC as location
    Local Instance LCT Using C_PHYLCT
    LCT = NewInstance C_PHYLCT AllocGroup null
    Local Char PROPERTIES(GLONAVA)(1..1)
    Local Char VALUES(255)        (1..1)
    Local Integer RET
    [L]PROPERTIES(1) = "GEOLOC"
    [L]RET = fmet LCT.GET_PROPERTIES_VALUE(PARAM.TRFLCTCOD, [L]PROPERTIES, [L]VALUES)
    If VALUES(1) <> AVOID.ACHAR
      this.GEOLOC = VALUES(1)
    Endif
    FreeGroup LCT
  # End issue 110304 & 114755
  Endif

  # Physical asset linked to a fixed asset and not an accounting validation

  # X3-55206
  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")

  If [L]ARET_VALUE = [V]CST_AOK
    If PARAM.FASFLG = [V]CST_ANO
      If (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET() and [L]B_FINANCIAL_TRF = [V]CST_ATRUE)
        [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(8,[V]CST_MSGPHY, 1), [V]CST_AWARNING)
      Else
        Local Char ERRMSG(250)
        [L]ERRMSG = func ASYRFNC.MES1(mess(171,[V]CST_MSGPHY, 1), this.PHYREF)
        [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", [L]ERRMSG, [V]CST_ASUCCESS)
      Endif
    Endif
  Endif

#  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("") # X3-55206

Return

#**
#* _PHYELT_CNL_TRANSFER  -  Physical asset transfer cancellation
#*
#* Transfer cancellation for a physical element that is "effectivly" transfered.
#*      A - Physical asset is not linked to a fixed asset
#*          The physical asset is modified. The transfer date is recalculated and an extourn event is created
#*      B - Physical is linked to a fixed asset
#*          i  - a pending movement for validation of the transfer exists. This movement is deleted
#*          ii - no pending movement, the physical asset is effectivily transfered.
#*               A pending movement for validation of the transfer cancellation is created
#*
#* @private
#* @param  PARAM      : PHYELTTRF data class instance contains parameters
#* @param                FASFLG(P) Fixed asset action (YES/NO)
#* @param                TRFDAT(RP*) Transfer date
#* @param                TRFTYP(RP*) Transfer type
#* @param                TRFLCTCOD(RP*) Localisation
#* @return Integer    : ARET_VALUE = [V]CST_AOK, [V]CST_AINFO, [V]CST_ASUCESS, [V]CST_AERROR, [V]CST_AFATAL
#* (*) Warning : proprieties of class used as static variable of the metod.
#*!
$_PHYELT_CNL_TRANSFER

  Local Integer STA, NUMMSG, I_TRFMVT, BRET, B_FINANCIAL_TRF
  Local Char ERRMSG(250), LCTCODO(GLONLCT), FCYO(GLONFCY), CPYO(GLONCPY)
  Local Date LSTTRFMVT_DAT

  [L]ARET_VALUE = [V]CST_AOK
  this.PHYTRF = [V]CST_ATRUE

  # 1°, we want to cancel the transfer (or cancel) movement
  # 2°, we want to cancel the last transfer (if not 1°)

  # 1°, pending movement for validation of the TRANSFER must be deleted
  # If found, no extourn movement is needed

  [L]I_TRFMVT = func _COLL_FIND_MVT(this, "PHYMVT", [V]CST_PMVGEO)
  If [L]I_TRFMVT = [V]CST_ANOTDEFINED
    # If not found, find a cancel transfer movement
    [L]I_TRFMVT = func _COLL_FIND_MVT(this, "PHYMVT", [V]CST_PMVAGEO)
  Endif
  # If a movement has been found, delete this
  If [L]I_TRFMVT <> [V]CST_ANOTDEFINED
    [L]STA = fmet this.ADELLINE("PHYMVT", [L]I_TRFMVT)
    [L]ERRMSG = func ASYRFNC.MES1(mess(193, [V]CST_MSGPHY, 1), this.PHYREF)
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", [L]ERRMSG, [V]CST_ASUCCESS)
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")

    # Quit cancel transfer is physical action
    If PARAM.FASFLG = [V]CST_ANO
      Return
    Endif
  Endif

  #--------------
  # Control
  #--------------

  If not (this.TRFDAT <> AVOID.ADATE)
    #**
    #* ==> If the physical asset is not linked to a fixed asset, it must have been transfered for cancelling transfer.
    #*     Therefore transfer date must be filled (ISSDAT)
    #*!
    If PARAM.FASFLG <> [V]CST_AYES
      [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(185,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
      Return
    Endif
  Endif

  If not (this.ISSDAT = AVOID.ADATE)
    #**
    #* ==> A physical asset cannot be cancel transfered if it is effectively issued (ISSDAT is filled).
    #*!
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(156,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
  Endif

  # Physical asset linked to a fixed asset
  If (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET())

    If PARAM.FASFLG = [V]CST_ANO
      If not (this.TRFDAT >= fmet this.ACTX.ACACHE.CNX.AGETVALDAT(this.CPY, 1, "CURFIYSTR"))
        #**
        #* ==> If the physical asset is effectivily transfered,
        #*     the transfer must not have been carried out in a previous fiscal year
        #*     Therefore the transfer date must be greater than or equal to
        #*     the beginning of the current fiscal year of the finance context .
        #*!
        [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(186, [V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
      Endif
      If func _COLL_FIND_MVT(this, "PHYMVT", [V]CST_PMVAGEO) <> CST_ANOTDEFINED
        #**
        #* ==> If the physical asset is effectivily transfered (ei ISSDAT is filled),
        #*     if a cancelation transfer pending movement exists it cannot be cancelled twice
        #*!
        [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", mess(188,[V]CST_MSGPHY,1), [V]CST_AERROR)
      Endif
    Endif

  Endif

  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")
  If ([L]ARET_VALUE >= [V]CST_AERROR) : Return : Endif

  #--------------
  # Execution
  #--------------
  # Event reversal : transfer of a physical asset
  Local Char EVT_ERRMSG(250)
  Local Instance EVT Using C_EVENT : EVT = NewInstance C_EVENT AllocGroup null

  EVT.EVTINT  = "PHYAFFGEO"
  [L]STA = fmet EVT.INIT_EVENT()

  EVT.REF     = this.PHYREF
  EVT.TIMSTP  = AVOID.ACHAR
  EVT.CPY     = this.CPY
  EVT.LIN     = 0
  EVT.PLAN    = [V]CST_PLNAUC
  EVT.EFFDAT  = this.TRFDAT
  If EVT.EFFDAT = AVOID.ADATE
    EVT.EFFDAT = PARAM.TRFDAT
  Endif
  If EVT.REN = AVOID.ACHAR
    EVT.REN = PARAM.TRFTYP
  Endif

  # If it's not a financial transfer, there will not write movement : always transfer will be done

  # Retrieve the info's event
  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet EVT.GET_TABLE_VALUE("LCTCODO", [L]LCTCODO)
  If [L]ARET_VALUE >= [V]CST_AERROR
    [L]BRET = func FXDFCT_SYRA.COPY_MSG(EVT, this)
  Endif

  [L]B_FINANCIAL_TRF = func IS_FINANCIAL_TRANSFER(this, [L]LCTCODO, [L]FCYO, [L]CPYO, [L]LSTTRFMVT_DAT)

  # Reversal of transfer event :
  # (Physical asset NOT linked to a fixed asset )
  # (               OR  (linked without pending movement and asked by fixed asset)
  #                 OR it wasn't a financial transfer

  If not (fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET()) or (PARAM.FASFLG = [V]CST_AYES) or ([L]B_FINANCIAL_TRF = [V]CST_AFALSE)

    [L]STA = fmet EVT.EXT_EVENT()
    If [L]STA = [V]CST_AOK
      #**
      #* WARNING : keep the infos (in PARAM class) for a physical asset which need a transfer (without an old one)
      #* PARAM.TRFDAT, PARAM.TRFTYP and PARAM.TRFLCTCOD must be set
      #*!
      If this.TRFDAT <> AVOID.ADATE and PARAM.TRFDAT = AVOID.ADATE
        PARAM.TRFDAT = this.TRFDAT
      Endif
      If PARAM.TRFTYP = AVOID.ACHAR
        [L]STA = fmet EVT.GET_TABLE_VALUE("REN", PARAM.TRFTYP)
      Endif
      # Retrieve the info's event (for doing an transfer event for a physical asset linked after the transfer)
      this.LCTCOD = [L]LCTCODO
      PARAM.TRFLCTCOD = this.LCTCOD
      this.FCY = [L]FCYO
      this.TRFDAT = func EVENT_CSTD.GET_DATE_PREVIOUS_EVENT(EVT)
    Elsif [L]STA = [V]CST_AWARNING and PARAM.FASFLG = [V]CST_AYES
      #**
      #* Event not found
      #* It's asked by fixed asset, so we do a transfer (if we have the needed infos)
      #*!
      [L]STA = fmet this._PHYELT_TRANSFER(PARAM)
    Else
      [L]BRET = func FXDFCT_SYRA.COPY_MSG(EVT, this)
      [L]ARET_VALUE = [V]CST_AERROR
      Return
    Endif

  Endif

  # If not asked by fixed asset for a linked physicxal asset :
    # and if it was a financial transfer
  # Pending movement must be created (if no pending movement has been deleted)
  If fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET() and PARAM.FASFLG <> [V]CST_AYES and [L]B_FINANCIAL_TRF = [V]CST_ATRUE
    # Pending movement for validation of the TRANSFER cancellation must be generated
    Local Integer LIN
    [L]LIN = fmet this.ADDLINE("PHYMVT", [V]CST_ALASTPOS)
    this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).NUM       = [L]LIN
    this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVT       = [V]CST_PMVAGEO
    this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTDAT    = this.TRFDAT
    this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTTRANS  = EVT.REN
    this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTFCY    = this.FCY
    this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTLCTCOD = this.LCTCOD
#    this.PHYMVT([L]LIN).MVTISSTYP = 0
  Endif

  FreeGroup EVT
  # X3-55206
  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")

  If [L]ARET_VALUE < [V]CST_AERROR
    Local Char ERRMSG(250)
    If fmet this.IS_LINKED_ASSET() and PARAM.FASFLG <> [V]CST_AYES and [L]B_FINANCIAL_TRF = [V]CST_ATRUE
      [L]ERRMSG = func ASYRFNC.MES1(mess(213,[V]CST_MSGPHY, 1), this.PHYREF)
      [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", [L]ERRMSG, [V]CST_AWARNING)
    Else
      [L]ERRMSG = func ASYRFNC.MES1(mess(187,[V]CST_MSGPHY, 1), this.PHYREF)
      [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ASETERROR("", [L]ERRMSG, [V]CST_ASUCCESS)
    Endif
  Endif

  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")

Return


#**
#* ================================
#* Private Method: _PHYELT_DEL_ALL_MVT - Pending movement deletion.
#* --------------------------------
#* Deletion of all pending movement of a physical asset.
#* If the physical asset is linked to a fixed asset, delete all the pending movements.
#* --------------------------------
#* @private
#* @return ARET_VALUE : [V]CST_AOK if OK, else [V]CST_AERROR (check error message stack)
#*!
$_PHYELT_DEL_ALL_MVT
  Local Integer STA
  Local Integer STACK_ERROR
  [L]ARET_VALUE= [V]CST_AOK

  #--------------
  # Control
  #--------------

  #--------------
  # Execution
  #--------------

  # Delete all pending movements
  Local Integer LIN
  For [L]LIN = maxtab(this.PHYMVT) To 1 Step -1
    [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.ADELLINE("PHYMVT", [L]LIN)
  Next [L]LIN

  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")

Return


# ======================================================================
#    P R I V A T E     O P E R A T I O N S
# ======================================================================

#**
#* ====================================
#* Private Operation: _PHYELT_ISSUE_OPE  -  Physical asset disposal
#* ------------------------------------
#* Physical asset disposal (an empty PHYLELT instance exists).
#*      1. Physical asset is read
#*      2- Private method _PHYELT_ISSUE is processed
#*      3- Physical asset is updated
#* ------------------------------------
#* @private
#* @param  PHYREF     : Physical asset reference
#* @param  PARAM      : PHYELTISS data class instance contains parameters
#* @param               ISSDAT : Disposal date
#* @param               ISSTYP : Disposal reason
#* @return ARET_VALUE : [V]CST_AOK if OK, else [V]CST_AERROR (check error message stack)
#*!
$_PHYELT_ISSUE_OPE

Local Integer BRET
  [L]ARET_VALUE= [V]CST_AOK

  # Read physical asset
  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AREAD(PHYREF)
  If ([L]ARET_VALUE >= [V]CST_AERROR) : Return : Endif

  this.ORIACT = PARAM.ORIACT : # PHYELT.ORIACT inherates the one from PARAM

  # Physical asset issue - Method
  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this._PHYELT_ISSUE(PARAM)
  # Copying messages from PHY class stack to PARAM class stack
  # because the stack will be deleted after call the AUPDATE method
  [L]BRET = func FXDFCT_SYRA.COPY_MSG(this, PARAM)

  If ([L]ARET_VALUE >= [V]CST_AERROR) : Return : Endif

  # Update physical asset
  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AUPDATE
  [L]ARET_VALUE = fmet this.AGETMAXERROR("")

Return

#**
#* ====================================
#* Private Operation: _PHYELT_CNL_ISSUE_OPE  -  Physical asset issue cancellation
#* ------------------------------------
#* Physical asset issue cancellation (an empty PHYELT instance exists).
#*      1. Physical asset is read
#*      2- Private method _PHYELT_CNL_ISSUE is processed
#*      3- Physical asset is updated
#* ------------------------------------
#* @private
#* @param  PHYREF     : Physical asset reference
#* @return ARET_VALUE : [V]CST_AOK if OK, else [V]CST_AERROR (check error message stack)
