#* ====================================
#* Private Operation: _PHYELT_CNL_TRANSFER_OPE  -  Physical asset transfer cancellation
#* ------------------------------------
#* Physical asset transfer cancellation (an empty PHYELT instance exists).
#*      1. Physical asset is read
#*      2- Private method _PHYELT_CNL_TRANSFER is processed
#*      3- Physical asset is updated
#* ------------------------------------
#* @private
#* @param  PHYREF     : Physical asset reference
#* @return ARET_VALUE : [V]CST_AOK if OK, else [V]CST_AERROR (check error message stack)
